token : 
 1 : header : its an object 
       carry the algorithm and the token ype 
 2 : payload : it's an object also but it carry some data related to the user ; may be user name and id 
       but not the password bcz its can be decoded 
 3 : signature :  takes the header and the payload and add the secret strund and hash all these data 
    - it is something unique that differntiate from token to another 
    - we use jwt pakage from npm 
    - jwt =>  
